\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59c7d8b1ff24cfae32e93f5afc15abb0d065153","tid":1199152,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T12:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114146ab017900e6db93bd66ab8eae6dc4053aa1","tid":1199152,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51f23a4d7ff6ec464db3956f2fc24040873fec2","tid":1199152,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943d0735d6fe3b7fb55a994a809ee4ea05d92cfd","tid":1199152,"uid":52276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推！！全港咁多信耶穌得永生嘅基督徒，主叫你係世上要作鹽作光！<br />\n馬太福音5章13節<br />\n你們是世上的鹽。鹽若失了味，怎能叫他再鹹呢？以後無用，不過丟在外面，被人踐踏了。<br />\n<br />\n你地活在世上唔出黎為主作見證，為公義發聲，就只係一件垃圾，係一件冇用嘅垃圾，冇存在嘅價值<br />\n快啲被主寵召啦"},{"pid":"00e4e56b71d14e690402c1039c0a77bf70b598c4","tid":1199152,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:27:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">   我只係想講好多基督徒出左黎 </span>"},{"pid":"a8c359aaef09e3d70912e43c6c4720eeef57728e","tid":1199152,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00e4e56b71d14e690402c1039c0a77bf70b598c4","tid":1199152,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:27:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">   我只係想講好多基督徒出左黎 </span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"好多人唔講姐<br />\n尋日出去,我身邊好多朋友都係基督徒"},{"pid":"3c8dad4272185a23e090556c5f8ba0f8740a68c7","tid":1199152,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/